# The native daemon is COMPILED from the phinet Rust source by
# ./build-android.sh — it's a build output, not source. Committing the
# prebuilt .so would mean anyone cloning this repo runs an anonymity daemon
# they didn't build and can't check against the source. Build it instead.
/app/src/main/jniLibs/

# Keep the Gradle wrapper — it's how a fresh clone builds with the right
# Gradle version. (Many templates ignore *.jar and silently drop it.)
!gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar
